# Normalize line endings across platforms.
# The *.sh / *.py shims are pulled into the binary via //go:embed and executed in the
# Linux codespace, so they MUST stay LF even on Windows checkouts (a CRLF shebang like
# '#!/usr/bin/env bash\r' fails to exec). Pinning eol=lf also keeps gofmt clean on Windows.
* text=auto eol=lf
*.png binary
*.exe binary
